title: Child Care Eligibility Specialist Interview
Application Type: I applied online. The process took 2 weeks. I interviewed at Child Development Associates (San Diego, CA) in Aug 2020
Interview Descriptions: Interview process was pretty straightforward, as long as you show you are a quick learner and organized you have a good chance, you must have some type of administrative experience to qualify.
Interview Questions: What administrative experience did I have

title: Payment Analyst Interview
Application Type: I applied online. The process took 3 months. I interviewed at Child Development Associates (Bonita, CA) in Sept 2016
Interview Descriptions: Process could be something slow, but it worth it. I was contact after applied online and was programmed for an interview in two weeks, then programmed to take test in another two weeks and receive a respond three weeks later to start working another three weeks later.
Interview Questions: Organization skill, Strong and Weakness, Interpersonal Relations

title: Childcare Eligibility Specialist Interview
Application Type: I applied online. The process took 3 weeks. I interviewed at Child Development Associates (San Diego, CA) in Sept 2011
Interview Descriptions: Submitted online application was then called to interview. Employment verification was done through  a third party. Skills tested included typing, 10 key and basic math. Interview panel, multiple candidates were interviewed.
Interview Questions:
What would I do if a client was distressed? How would I handle the situation?

How would I handle a conflict with a co-worker? Have I had a conflict in the past?
